From: Peter Freyd <pjf@saul.cis.upenn.edu>
Message-Id: <200009061743.e86HhCQ25057@saul.cis.upenn.edu>
To: categories@mta.ca
Subject: categories: Barr question
Sender: cat-dist@mta.ca
Precedence: bulk
Status: O
