Subject: categories: Tech report: Models for Name-Passing Processes
Date: Fri, 29 Sep 2000 15:20:54 +0100
From: Luca Cattani <Luca.Cattani@cl.cam.ac.uk>
Message-Id: <E13f11z-0002i9-00@wisbech.cl.cam.ac.uk>
